    m_mu - 1sigma: m_tau pred (MeV)        269.46082257
    Spread from m_mu uncertainty (MeV)     0.0

  The m_tau prediction sensitivity to m_mu is sub-MeV.
  The dominant question is whether a^2 = 2 holds exactly,
  not the input mass precision.

